metadata.name: Pretty Girl, she has to be so pretty.
metadata.description:
Pretty Girl is a womanhood's tale. Inspired by Jackie Burkhart, but at its core a self portrait, I portrait a girl who for better or for worse finds refuge and safety in being pretty. Even in her most comfortable state, laying in her sanctuary surrounded by things she loves, she's still guarded.
I still don't know whether or not there is someone at the other side of the phone.
